{"type": "article", "id": 11661, "title": "Mansur Gavriel & Colette 联名水桶包", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-06T11:30:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000135GgFajbWxzHDZEush.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tRachel Mansur 和 Floriana Gavriel 前几日刚刚把 2015 年 Swarovski 设计大奖搬回家，从去年开始全球大热的水桶包品牌 Mansur Gavriel 和法国时尚品牌 Colette 便将推出合作系列，这是一款宝蓝色带有亮片的水桶包，缀有 Mansur Gavriel 标志性的蝴蝶结。这是 Mansur Gavriel 第一次国际合作，预计售价 635 欧元，今日开始上线，<a href=\"http://www.colette.fr/marques/mansur-gavriel.html\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135749alwm3QCV7xRGMPvL.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"675\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<br>\r\n<span></span><span></span>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135749CLOQjdMTGKRB8NV4.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"810\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135750DI7EAk0dwP9tJa1F.jpg\" width=\"760\" height=\"507\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66710526\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}